mg class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148210/extras/PotionMixing.gif?t=1737666049\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Element-Based Magic System</strong><br>Harness the power of elemental magic to dominate your enemies. Swap characters and use your arsenal of combat tools to exploit weaknesses for maximum damage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148210/extras/Elements.gif?t=1737666049\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Post-Story Content</strong><br>The adventure doesn\u2019t end after the credits roll. Unlock additional content and challenges that keep the game fresh even after completing the main storyline.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Silly Easter Eggs &amp; References</strong><br>Expect <strong>plenty of inside jokes</strong> and nods to games, movies, and pop culture. It's serious when it needs to be... and hilarious when it doesn't!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2148210/extras/MetalTRex.png?t=1737666049\" /></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Developer\u2019s Journey</strong><br><strong>Developed by One Person</strong> \u2013 <strong>Made with a lot of caffeine, some sleep deprivation, and a healthy dose of stubbornness.</strong> It\u2019s a labor of love \u2014 raw, imperfect, but filled with passion. If you appreciate indie games that wear their heart on their sleeve, this one\u2019s for you.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">NOTES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> You might need to disable Steam Input for controllers to work properly, or try another template.</p></li></ul>","developers":["Godarkhaos"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id